Name: EXP (blessing)
Description:
Completing activity goals, commissions, and quests can earn experience. When the experience reaches a certain level, the Adventurer Level can be increased.
Increasing the Adventurer Level not only provides attribute boosts, bio-element gifts, and Talent Points.
